    summary: "Atraken is a devastated world destroyed during the Clone Wars — its oceans boiled away, air poisoned, and 90% of the population killed. Survivors fled to the moon Trilos, where 50,000 colonists now live in pressurized shelters mining ore. The planet surface is lethal: space suits degrade at 1D cumulative per hour vs 5D integrity, then 2D damage per 10 minutes exposed. Visibility is 20 meters. Unknown to the colonists, Trilos is home to the Ee — tiny sentient telepathic worms (1-6.5cm) with mental powers including memory alteration, telekinesis, and cell burst. The Ee have been secretly watching the Atrakenites, altering trader memories so tales of Trilos sound unbelievable. A salvaged X-wing sits at the starport, available for trade.",
