    ofNote: "Under strict Imperial quarantine — no one allowed to enter or leave. The KDY Class 1000 light cruiser Intrepid (300m, crew 580, 28 turbolasers, 12 ion cannons, commanded by Captain Dulrain) maintains orbit guarding both the quarantine and the prison asteroid. TIE fighter patrols the planet roughly half the time. Ships approaching without permission are engaged. Landing requires Difficult space transports roll if the Gesarils sense negative emotions; Moderate to escape back to orbit. Prison supply contract: 100 tons from Travnin every 50 days for 3,000 cr/run. Gesaril psychic carvings are potentially extremely valuable trade items — if the Empire doesn't discover their origin. One crashed ship reportedly carried a cloaking device."
