    ofNote: "Headquarters of the Tenloss Syndicate — one of the biggest non-Hutt criminal operations in the Outer Rim Territories, extending across 64 major star systems in the Astal, Bajic, Dail, Skine, and Lol sectors with an estimated 560,000+ employees. Little is known about its founder, Bandar Tenloss, beyond that the syndicate is governed by a Leukish (criminal board of directors) of unknown size and composition. The syndicate acts as intermediary between individual crime groups, the Empire, and even the New Republic. Three business principles: equal risks/equal profits, hostages as insurance, instant reprisal for betrayal. Tenloss employs an 'effective delegation of blame' — when operations go wrong, another criminal organization takes the fall."
