    summary: "Tangrene is one of the more heavily defended planets in the Empire's sphere of influence, largely due to the presence of an Imperial Ubiqtorate base housing one of the few crystal gravfield trap arrays near the New Republic border. That General Garm Bel Iblis managed a successful raid against the planet is a monument to the Corellian senator's cunning. Tangrene is a craggy, mountainous world almost completely devoid of surface vegetation and water. Underground lakes and one subterranean ocean have been tapped to supply the Imperial garrisons. These underground caverns support a wide diversity of fungi and vegetation, and glowing fern-like lake plants help provide a breathable, if thin, atmosphere.",
