    locations: "Imperial Shipyards (weapons design and starship construction facilities). Weapons Range (testing site; rumored to have been used for early prototypes of the Empire's torpedo spheres). Yagai Cave Networks (eroded through mountain chains on six continents; primary Yagai habitation).",
    ofNote: "The Old Republic used Yaga Minor as a launch point for the 'Outbound Flight' project — a valiant attempt to learn more about what lies beyond the galaxy. When the Empire arose, Yaga Minor was converted to strictly military use. The Yagai subspecies — large, strong aliens genetically engineered as a labor source suited for harsh environments — have been employed as cheap slave labor. They are quite knowledgeable about starship drives and weapons systems, making them an excellent source of construction conscripts. Yaga Minor has become of increasing importance to the Empire because of this labor pool."
