    summary: "Contrasts with its sister Bormean worlds in many ways. Although urban, Chandrila prides itself on its balance of developed areas and tended agriculture and agriforest zones. Most of the planet is developed for production, but the bulk is in agricombines, making Chandrila one of the last food exporters in the Core and one of the few with no oxygen factories.",
