    summary: "A quiet world noted mainly for its advanced medical facilities. Rhinnal was occupied by Esseles for centuries before the Empire arrived and the people saw no significant change in governing. Rhinnalians find their cultural identity in passive aggression — noted for exclusive attitudes toward fashion, behavior, and style, where no foreigner, particularly non-humans, can measure up to their standards.",
