    summary: "System governed by Serdif Tount under the supervision of Moff Lankin, governor of the strategic Lambda Sector. Under martial law with constant patrols of stormtroopers and Army troopers. The populace is unaware of the fall of the Empire and the rise of the New Republic.",
    locations: "",
    ofNote: "WANTED — SERDIF TOUNT: New Republic bounty of 35,000 credits. Wanted alive. Charges: treason, sedition, conspiracy to overthrow the New Republic government, murder of New Republic personnel, destruction of New Republic property. Tount has aided Moff Lankin in attacks on New Republic worlds, conquering three planets. Martial law is in effect — incoming traffic is thoroughly screened and individual liberties have been extinguished. New Republic spies report the populace is primed for revolt but lacks the courage to act. If Tount were taken, the whole sector might fall to the Republic. | CRACKEN'S PERSONAL NOTES: Informants have told us that the populace of Rintonne is not yet aware of the fall of the Empire and the rise of the New Republic. Tount's control of information is so great that he is able to enslave a whole population through fear alone. However, if our forces can show these people hope and prove that victories are possible, it might be enough to tip the balance to open revolt."
