    source: "WEG40062 Wanted by Cracken p.26",
    summary: "Homeworld of the Kerestians, including Andov Syn — a bounty hunter who specializes in hunting other bounty hunters. Syn appeared shortly after the establishment of the New Republic and has rapidly built a fearsome reputation.",
    locations: "",
    ofNote: "WANTED — ANDOV SYN: New Republic bounty of 60,000 credits. Dead or alive. Charges: murder of New Republic personnel, destruction of New Republic property, aiding and abetting known criminals, bribery. Syn is hired by fugitives to eliminate their pursuers — a bounty hunter who hunts other bounty hunters. He is best known for singlehandedly eliminating six mercenaries hired to protect a mining colony on Adim. Travels in a jet-black modified space yacht. | CRACKEN'S PERSONAL NOTES: Syn is ruthless, deadly and utterly without pity. He has carved a niche for himself in the underworld and considers himself the best at what he does. Syn has picked up a number of talents along the way and is far more than a standard manhunter. My warning to those of you who may seek the bounty on Andov Syn is, while you are hunting him, be sure that he is not hunting you as well."
